          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15409317/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15409317/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/neon007/" class=" " title="萝卜公公">萝卜公公</a>
                (阅读即生活，但不要忘记去思考)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="15409317">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">1  skinner , Intermittent reinforcement 间歇强迫，如爱情赌博等 
2 服从于权威，大多数人会无条件服从 
